      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BONDI BLOSSOM (4) has been beaten just over a length in her two runs this prep, the latest in a similar race to this here 11 days ago. Finished runner-up at her only other third-up run. Gets in with just 53kgs after the claim which might be enough to see her get the cash. Lightly raced filly CRATHIE KIRK (7) made up plenty of ground to finish third when fresh from a spell over 1200m at Port Macquarie last time out. Up in grade but drops 5.5kgs and should relish getting out to this distance for the first time. THE IRON STAR (3) settled worse than midfield before letting down impressively to collect his maiden win over this trip at Hawkesbury recently. Drawn to get a soft run and can compete at this higher level. SHOWTIME SHADOW (1) has been very good at all three runs this prep, the latest outing a narrow defeat over 1350m at Wyong. Hitting the line well so a bit more ground on a bigger track looks perfect. MCADAM (2) is ready to show some form third-up over a more suitable journey.",
